V0113_01_00_00_0.text:
Right on, soldier!
You got a Duel with a dino!

V0113_01_00_01_0.text:
Dinosaurs aren't extinct!
They live on inside me!

V0113_01_00_03_0.text: They'll be scraping ya off the ground with a squeegee!

V0113_01_00_04_0.text: I climbed the ranks - all thanks to you!

V0113_01_00_04_1.text: And I learned a few new tactics on the way, sarge!

V0113_01_00_05_1.text:
If I win, Jaden's MY wingman!
Got that?

V0113_01_00_06_0.text:
Fate?
I'll worry about that gibberish after the war's over!

V0113_03_00_00_0.text: I'll send ya back to the civilian life!

V0113_03_00_03_0.text: My prehistoric patrol isn’t through with you yet!

V0113_03_00_04_0.text: I can't afford anymore tactical errors!

V0113_05_00_00_0.text: Just like the sarge, I believe in my cards!

V0113_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0113_08_00_00_0.text:
Brace yourself!
I activate the Spell Card, Earthquake!

V0113_08_00_00_1.text: Every face-up monster is forced into Defense Position!

V0113_08_00_01_0.text:
It's the dawn of the dinos!
I activate Jurassic World!

V0113_08_00_01_1.text: This here's the definition of terrain advantage!

V0113_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Tail Swipe!

V0113_08_00_03_0.text: I activate my Equip Spell, Living Fossil!

V0113_08_00_04_0.text: Here's the Spell Card, Double Evolution Pill!

V0113_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Spacetime Transcendence!

V0113_08_00_06_0.text: I Tribute a Dinosaur to activate Big Evolution Pill!

V0113_08_00_06_1.text: With this in play, I can summon Dinos without Tributing!

V0113_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Ultra Evolution Pill!

V0113_08_00_07_1.text: It evolves reptiles into dinos in a snap!

V0113_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Fossil Dig!

V0113_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Field Spell, Wasteland!

V0113_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Raise Body Heat!

V0113_08_00_11_0.text: I invite ya to the land where dinos never went extinct!

V0113_08_00_11_1.text: I activate the Field Spell, Lost World!

V0113_08_00_13_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Jurassic Impact!

V0113_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Fossil Excavation!

V0113_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Hunting Instinct!

V0113_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Survival Instinct!

V0113_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Volcanic Eruption!

V0113_08_00_17_1.text: The molten lava destroys all cards on the field!

V0113_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my trap!
Jurrac Impact!

V0113_08_00_18_1.text: All cards on the field are extinct!

V0113_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my trap!
Survival's End!

V0113_08_00_20_0.text: I activate Survival's End's effect from my Graveyard!

V0113_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my trap!
Survival of the Fittest!

V0113_08_00_22_0.text: Survival of the Fittest lets my dinosaur attack again!

V0113_08_00_23_0.text: I activate my trap, Seismic Shockwave!

V0113_08_00_24_1.text: I return a Dinosaur in my Graveyard to my hand!

V0113_09_00_00_0.text: I activate Destroyersaurus's effect from my hand!

V0113_09_00_00_1.text: I add Jurassic World to my hand!

V0113_09_00_02_1.text: It sends the monster it battled back to the owner's hand!

V0113_09_00_04_1.text: When it's attacked, it switches to Defense Position!

V0113_09_00_05_0.text: Gilasaurus lets ya Special Summon a monster from your grave!

V0113_09_00_08_0.text: Ultimate Conductor Tyranno activates its effect!

V0113_09_00_10_0.text: Super-Ancient Dinobeast's effect lets me draw a card!

V0113_09_00_13_0.text: I activate Miscellaneousaurus's effect from my hand!

V0113_09_00_14_0.text: Miscellaneousaurus's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0113_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0113_13_00_04_0.text:
It's the start of a new era!
Tyranno Infinity!

V0113_13_00_05_0.text: I'm counting on ya, Hyper Hammerhead!

V0113_13_00_06_0.text:
This'll throw ya for a loop!
Babycerasaurus!

V0113_13_00_08_0.text:
Dark Driceratops!
Report to the field!

V0113_13_00_09_0.text:
Ultimate Tyranno!
Join the front lines!

V0113_13_00_11_0.text: Super Conductor Tyranno is reporting for duty!

V0113_13_00_13_0.text: Set your binoculars on the apex predator!

V0113_13_00_13_1.text: I Special Summon Ultimate Conductor Tyranno!

V0113_13_00_26_0.text: You won't stop my Mad Sword Beast!

V0113_16_00_00_0.text: Your Life Points are going AWOL!

V0113_19_00_15_0.text:
Super-Ancient Dinobeast!
Lay on the hurt!

V0113_21_00_00_0.text: You and your squadron'll be extinct in no time!

V0113_28_00_00_0.text:
Mission accomplished!
All thanks to my dino DNA!

V0113_28_00_01_0.text: The sarge helped evolve my Dueling to new heights!

V0113_28_00_02_0.text: If I can survive the Jurassic Period, I can survive you!

V0113_28_00_03_0.text: With my dino DNA, I'm stronger than your average Joe!

V0113_28_00_04_0.text: I couldn'ta built a deck this mighty without your help!

V0113_28_00_04_1.text: I owe everything to ya, sarge!

V0113_28_00_05_0.text: You can leave the sarge's sidekick gig to me, junior!

V0113_28_00_06_0.text: This soldier isn't down with your destiny talk!

V0113_28_00_06_1.text: You think words can harm a dino?

V0113_29_00_00_0.text: Yowzer! Now that was a good 'ol fashioned hind whoopin'!

V0113_29_00_02_0.text: My Dueling will keep evolving, so I won't lose next time!

V0113_29_00_04_0.text: You're a T-Rex compared to my plant munchin' Stegosaurus.

V0113_29_00_06_0.text: You're the scariest Duelist east of the Rio Grande, ma'am!

V0113_33_00_00_0.text: Feast your eyes on dino power!

V0113_34_00_00_0.text: No one gets between me and my commanding officer!

V0113_34_00_01_0.text: I gotta hand it to ya - can't let my guard down!

V0113_34_00_02_0.text: This is the toughness that allowed the dinos to survive!

V0113_34_00_03_0.text: My heart's about to erupt like a volcano!

V0113_34_00_05_0.text: You're not much of a Duelist, but I like your style!

V0113_34_00_07_0.text: You haven't seen the best of my dino combos yet!

V0113_34_00_08_0.text: I'm the only Duelist with a dinosaur bone in his leg!

V0113_34_00_09_0.text: I'm evolvin' into a galaxy-flyin' Spacesaurus!

V0113_35_00_00_0.text: No one's more dino than me!

V0113_36_00_00_0.text: I'm glad you're in my platoon! You're as bad as a bronto!

V0113_36_00_03_0.text: When the sarge's in charge, I can take a furlough!

V0113_36_00_04_0.text: I know I can count on you, sarge!

V0113_36_00_05_0.text: I know you'll execute your tactics, sarge!

V0113_36_00_08_0.text: I know you're up to the task, private!

V0113_36_00_09_0.text: The success of this mission is in your hands, ma'am!

V0113_36_00_11_0.text: Uh... Hope you're not mad at me, ma'am.
